<Layout title="Privacy Policy - GamesMobZone">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12 max-w-4xl pt-32 md:pt-40">
    <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-8 text-primary uppercase">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-lg text-app-text prose-invert max-w-none">
      <p class="mb-4 text-app-muted">Last updated: November 23, 2025</p>
      <p>
        Gamesmobzone team has adopted this privacy policy (“Privacy Policy”) to
        explain how gamesmobzone collects, stores, and uses the information
        collected in connection with gamesmobzone’s Services.
      </p>

      <p class="font-bold text-lg mt-6">
        BY INSTALLING, USING, REGISTERING TO OR OTHERWISE ACCESSING THE
        SERVICES, YOU AGREE TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY AND GIVE AN EXPLICIT AND
        INFORMED CONSENT TO THE PROCESSING OF YOUR PERSONAL DATA IN ACCORDANCE
        WITH THIS PRIVACY POLICY. IF YOU DO NOT AGREE TO THIS PRIVACY POLICY,
        PLEASE DO NOT INSTALL, USE, REGISTER TO OR OTHERWISE ACCESS THE
        SERVICES.
      </p>
      <p>
        gamesmobzone reserves the right to modify this Privacy Policy at
        reasonable times, so please review it frequently. If gamesmobzone makes
        material or significant changes to this Privacy Policy, gamesmobzone may
        post a notice on gamesmobzone’s website along with the updated Privacy
        Policy. Your continued use of Services will signify your acceptance of
        the changes to this Privacy Policy.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4 text-primary">
        Non-personal data
      </h2>
      <p>
        For purposes of this Privacy Policy, “non-personal data” means
        information that does not directly identify you. The types of
        non-personal data gamesmobzone may collect and use include, but are not
        limited to: application properties, including, but not limited to
        application name, package name and icon installed on your device. Your
        checkin (include like, recommendation) of a game will be disclosed to
        all gamesmobzone users.
      </p>
      <p>
        gamesmobzone may use and disclose to gamesmobzone’s partners and
        contractors the collected non-personal data for purposes of analyzing
        usage of the Services, advertisement serving, managing and providing the
        Services and to further develop the Services and other gamesmobzone
        services and products.
      </p>
      <p>
        You recognize and agree that the analytics companies utilized by
        gamesmobzone may combine the information collected with other
        information they have independently collected from other services or
        products relating to your activities. These companies collect and use
        information under their own privacy policies.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4 text-primary">
        Personal Data
      </h2>
      <p>
        For purposes of this Privacy Policy, “personal data” means personally
        identifiable information that specifically identifies you as an
        individual.
      </p>
      <p>
        Personal information collected by gamesmobzone is information
        voluntarily provided to us by you when you create your account or change
        your account information. The information includes your facebook id,
        name, gender, location and your friends’id on facebook. gamesmobzone
        also stores your game checkins, likes, dislikes, recommendations and
        messages.
      </p>
      <p>
        gamesmobzone may use collected personal data for purposes of analyzing
        usage of the Services, providing customer and technical support,
        managing and providing Services (including managing advertisement
        serving) and to further develop the Services and other gamesmobzone
        services and products. gamesmobzone may combine non-personal data with
        personal data.
      </p>
      <p>
        Please note that certain features of the Services may be able to connect
        to your social networking sites to obtain additional information about
        you. In such cases, gamesmobzone may be able to collect certain
        information from your social networking profile when your social
        networking site permits it, and when you consent to allow your social
        networking site to make that information available to gamesmobzone. This
        information may include, but is not limited to, your name, profile
        picture, gender, user ID, email address, your country, your language,
        your time zone, the organizations and links on your profile page, the
        names and profile pictures of your social networking site “friends” and
        other information you have included in your social networking site
        profile. gamesmobzone may associate and/or combine as well as use
        information collected by gamesmobzone and/or obtained through such
        social networking sites in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4 text-primary">
        Disclosure and Transfer of Personal Data
      </h2>
      <p>
        gamesmobzone collects and processes personal data on a voluntary basis
        and it is not in the business of selling your personal data to third
        parties. Personal data may, however, occasionally be disclosed in
        accordance with applicable legislation and this Privacy Policy.
        Additionally, gamesmobzone may disclose personal data to its parent
        companies and its subsidiaries in accordance with this Privacy Policy.
      </p>
      <p>
        gamesmobzone may hire agents and contractors to collect and process
        personal data on gamesmobzone’s behalf and in such cases such agents and
        contractors will be instructed to comply with our Privacy Policy and to
        use personal data only for the purposes for which the third party has
        been engaged by gamesmobzone. These agents and contractors may not use
        your personal data for their own marketing purposes. gamesmobzone may
        use third party service providers such as credit card processors, e-mail
        service providers, shipping agents, data analyzers and business
        intelligence providers. gamesmobzone has the right to share your
        personal data as necessary for the aforementioned third parties to
        provide their services for gamesmobzone. gamesmobzone is not liable for
        the acts and omissions of these third parties, except as provided by
        mandatory law.
      </p>
      <p>
        gamesmobzone may disclose your personal data to third parties as
        required by law enforcement or other government officials in connection
        with an investigation of fraud, intellectual property infringements, or
        other activity that is illegal or may expose you or gamesmobzone to
        legal liability. gamesmobzone may also disclose your personal data to
        third parties when gamesmobzone has a reason to believe that a
        disclosure is necessary to address potential or actual injury or
        interference with gamesmobzone’s rights, property, operations, users or
        others who may be harmed or may suffer loss or damage, or gamesmobzone
        believes that such disclosure is necessary to protect gamesmobzone ’s
        rights, combat fraud and/or comply with a judicial proceeding, court
        order, or legal process served on gamesmobzone. To the extent permitted
        by applicable law, gamesmobzone will make reasonable efforts to notify
        you of such disclosure through gamesmobzone’s website or in another
        reasonable manner.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4 text-primary">Safeguards</h2>
      <p>
        gamesmobzone follows generally accepted industry standards and maintains
        reasonable safeguards to attempt to ensure the security, integrity and
        privacy of the information in gamesmobzone’s possession. Only those
        persons with a need to process your personal data in connection with the
        fulfillment of their tasks in accordance with the purposes of this
        Privacy Policy and for the purposes of performing technical maintenance,
        have access to your personal data in gamesmobzone’s possession. Personal
        data collected by gamesmobzone is stored in secure operating
        environments that are not available to the public. To prevent
        unauthorized on-line access to personal data, gamesmobzone maintains
        personal data behind a firewall-protected server. However, no system can
        be 100% secure and there is the possibility that despite gamesmobzone’s
        reasonable efforts, there could be unauthorized access to your personal
        data. By using the Services, you assume this risk.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4 text-primary">
        Other Provisions
      </h2>
      <p>
        Please be aware of the open nature of certain social networking and
        other open features of the Services gamesmobzone may make available to
        you. You may choose to disclose data about yourself in the course of
        contributing user generated content to the Services. Any data that you
        disclose in any of these forums, blogs, chats or the like is public
        information, and there is no expectation of privacy or confidentiality.
        gamesmobzone is not responsible for any personal data you choose to make
        public in any of these forums.
      </p>
      <p>
        If you are under 15 years of age or a minor in your country of
        residence, please ask your legal guardian’s permission to use or access
        the Services. gamesmobzone takes children’s privacy seriously, and
        encourages parents and/or guardians to play an active role in their
        children’s online experience at all times. gamesmobzone does not
        knowingly collect any personal information from children below the
        aforementioned age and if gamesmobzone learns that gamesmobzone has
        inadvertently gathered personal data from children under the
        aforementioned age, gamesmobzone will take reasonable measures to
        promptly erase such personal data from gamesmobzone’s records.
      </p>
      <p>
        gamesmobzone may store and/or transfer your personal data to its
        affiliates and partners in and outside of EU/EEA member states and the
        United States in accordance with mandatory legislation and this Privacy
        Policy. gamesmobzone may disclose your personal data to third parties in
        connection with a corporate merger, consolidation, restructuring, the
        sale of substantially all of gamesmobzone’s stock and/or assets or other
        corporate change, including, without limitation, during the course of
        any due diligence process provided, however, that this Privacy Policy
        shall continue to govern such personal data.
      </p>
      <p>
        gamesmobzone regularly reviews its compliance with this Privacy Policy.
        If gamesmobzone receives a formal written complaint from you, it is
        gamesmobzone’s policy to attempt to contact you directly to address any
        of your concerns. gamesmobzone will cooperate with the appropriate
        governmental authorities, including data protection authorities, to
        resolve any complaints regarding the collection, use, transfer or
        disclosure of personal data that cannot be amicably resolved between you
        and gamesmobzone.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4 text-primary">
        3rd party services
      </h2>
      <p>
        We use 3rd party services in our apps. These services collect usage data
        in compliance with their Privacy Policies. The services are described
        below.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2 text-primary">Advertising</h3>
      <p>
        3rd party ad serving systems allow user data to be utilized for
        advertising communication purposes displayed in the form of banners and
        other advertisements on gamesmobzone apps, possibly based on user
        interests.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2 text-primary">
        Data Sharing
      </h3>
      <p>
        We do not sell any data to third parties. We may share data with third
        parties to improve your user experience. The app does use third party
        services that may collect information used to identify you.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2 text-primary">
        Link to privacy policy of third party service providers used by the app
      </h3>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
        <li>Google Play Services</li>
        <li>Firebase Analytics</li>
        <li>Unity Ads</li>
        <li>IronSource</li>
        <li>Facebook</li>
        <li>Applovin</li>
        <li>Admob</li>
      </ul>

      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-6 mb-2 text-primary">Analytics</h3>
      <p>
        3rd party analytics services allow us to monitor and analyze app usage,
        better understand our audience and user behavior.
      </p>
      <p class="mt-4">
        Google Analytics is an analysis service provided by Google Inc. Google
        utilizes the collected data to track and examine the use of gamesmobzone
        Apps, to prepare reports on user activities and share them with other
        Google services. Google may use the data to contextualize and
        personalize the ads of its own advertising network. (<a
          href="http://www.google.com/intl/en/policies/privacy/"
          target="_blank"
          class="text-accent hover:text-primary transition"
          >http://www.google.com/intl/en/policies/privacy/</a
        >)
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-2 text-primary">
        Children’s Online Privacy Protection Act Compliance (COPPA)
      </h3>
      <p>
        We are in compliance with the requirements of COPPA, we do not collect
        any personal information from anyone under 13 years of age. Our products
        and services are all directed to people who are at least 13 years old or
        older.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-3xl font-semibold mt-10 mb-4 text-primary">Contact Us</h2>
      <p>
        If you have any questions about this privacy policy or our privacy
        practices, please contact us.
      </p>
      <p class="font-bold">
        mail: <a
          href="mailto:info@gamesmobzone.com"
          class="text-accent hover:text-primary transition"
          >info@gamesmobzone.com</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
